    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Where engagements tend to land.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:70ch;">Illustrative only &mdash; not quotes, not real clients. Your retainer is scoped per engagement after the discovery call and confirmed in writing.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
